sequenceDiagram
    actor Browser
    participant RL as RateLimitInterceptor
    participant API as Spring Boot

    Browser->>RL: POST /api/chat/stream

    RL->>RL: Resolve IP from X-Forwarded-For (rightmost) or RemoteAddr

    RL->>RL: Per-minute bucket (5 req/min per IP)
    alt Minute limit exceeded
        RL-->>Browser: 429 RATE_LIMITED
    end

    RL->>RL: Daily bucket (20 req/day per IP)
    alt Daily limit exceeded
        RL-->>Browser: 429 DAILY_RATE_LIMITED
    end

    RL->>API: Pass through
    API-->>Browser: Normal response

    Note over RL: Minute buckets cleared every 10 min
    Note over RL: Daily buckets cleared at midnight UTC
